data.description: RARE FIND! This home is unique, centrally located, and ready for its new family. The main floor features a great open-concept layout. You'll find a nice sized kitchen, dining space, family room and bathroom on the main floor. The upper level has two bedrooms, each with their own bathroom attached! The closets are spacious and the primary bedroom even features a nice deck to enjoy your morning coffee on. The washer and dryer are conveniently located on the upper level between the two bedrooms. Outside you'll love the LARGE fenced yard and garden shed! The front patio is adorable and perfect for a comfy outdoor sofa and chair. Call today for your private showing!
